OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and cool day in the
OL,6,Feast with rain at times, possibly
OL,7,Fheavy at first. A little rain at first
OL,8,Fin the west then, bright, sunny and
OL,9,Fwarm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be cloudy for most
OL,12,Fwith some patchy light drizzle at
OL,13,Ftimes. Staying dry in the southwest
OL,14,Fwith some evening sunshine, then clear
OL,15,Fspells overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FBright or sunny spells to
OL,18,Fstart in the southwest, otherwise a
OL,19,Fcloudy start. Then brightening up with
OL,20,Fsunny intervals developing for all.
OL,21,FVery warm in west, cooler east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
