OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,6,Fto Wednesday will be dry, sunny and
OL,7,Fvery warm in the west. Dry and cooler
OL,8,Fin the east, cloudier at times but
OL,9,Fstill plenty of sunny spells by day.
